      <title>特朗普就任前，中国副主席会见马斯克</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/chinese-vice-president-meets-musk-just-before-trump-takes-office</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国家副主席韩正会见亿万富翁埃隆·马斯克和其他美国商界人士，强调北京方面在当选总统唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫前为中美关系奠定积极基调的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/chinese-vice-president-meets-musk-just-before-trump-takes-office</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 03:57:33 GMT</pubDate>
